        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-01-25T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-01-25T17:00:00-05:00" n="1036" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1036">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 E.W./1–2545: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Paraguay</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Beaulac</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Asunción</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-01-25T18:00:00-04:00">January 25, 1945—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received January 26—9:46 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>63. I discussed instruction 86 of January 11 with Chiriani today. He approves and
                    will make strong favorable recommendation to President.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Beaulac</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
